My passion lies in bike riding.
i always want to ride the new bikes ,want to get the details of the bikes that releases recently etc..
so i want to make an app where a person like me can get to know the details of the particular bike,its specifications,the maintainance one should take care of his bike,ongoing trend,optimal usage etc..
a place where one who is going to buy bike can find all talks regarding that bike.He can compare with any other bike to see which is better.
